import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Carousel, Image } from 'react-bootstrap'

const ProductCarousel = ({ }) => {

	return (
		<Carousel pause='hover' className='bg-light' style={{ height: '35vh' }}>
			<Carousel.Item style={{ height: '35vh' }} interval={5000}>
				<Link >
					<Image style={{ height: '130%', width: '1000%' }}
						className="d-block w-100" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQvNz3iUa2QlQPDVRRsB0G12Y0JnUFGKzb4yQ&s" fluid />
				</Link>
			</Carousel.Item>
			<Carousel.Item style={{ height: '35vh' }} interval={5000}>
				<Link >
					<Image style={{ height: '100%', width: '100%', objectFit: 'cover' }}
						className="d-block w-100" src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/neoncolored-laptop-cover-futuristic-computer-technology-projects-wallpapers-concept-futuristic-technology-neon-colors-computer-accessories-laptop-covers-wallpaper-design_918839-252101.jpg" fluid />
				</Link>
			</Carousel.Item>
			<Carousel.Item style={{ height: '35vh' }} interval={5000}>
				<Link >
					<Image style={{ height: '100%', width: '100%', objectFit: 'cover' }}
						className="d-block w-100" src="https://www.easeus.com/images/en/wiki-news/dual-monitors-dual.png" fluid />
				</Link>
			</Carousel.Item>
		</Carousel>
	)
}

export default ProductCarousel
